</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kagebu>Kagebu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(4/19/03 2:18:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1098.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://liquid2k.com/datenshidojo/sano01.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Namakura</span><hr size=1> Yeah, I am writing it in English. Thanks for the help, both of you, and I'll be using Namakura as the name of his weapon, then. I'm hoping to get this thing published and it be popular enough that it might be translated into Japanese and sell in Japan (I plan on becoming a fairly recognizable author.)<br>
I'm not so sure how well the Japanese people would percieve my works, since most of them are based in Japan (Datenshi and The Kaishuu Project, at least)<br>
<br>
Thanks, again. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.datenshidojo.cjb.net" target="top">Datenshi Online</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aohjpn>aohjpn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(4/19/03 6:15:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1098.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Namakura</span><hr size=1> OK! For further information, &quot;namakura&quot; itself can be  used as a known. That is, this word can be used like Ç±Ç¢Ç¬ÇÕÇ»Ç‹Ç≠ÇÁÇæ(koitsu wa namakura da)[This is a &quot;namakura = a useless thing/guy/fellow&quot;].<br>
